name: Checklist: Add courses
intro:
When you feel you understand the following aspects of Moodle admin, select 'I can do these'.

  • I understand how to set course defaults for my site
  • I understand how to add courses one at a time
  • I understand how to bulk add courses (course settings)
  • I understand in general terms the activities available to teachers in courses

name: Checklist: Add users
intro:
When you feel you understand the following aspects of Moodle admin, select 'I can do these'.

  • I understand the concepts of roles and permissions
  • I understand the difference between authentication and enrolment
  • I understand the various ways of adding users to a site and a course
  • I understand how to use cohorts and groups

name: Checklist: Customize your site
intro:
When you feel you understand the following aspects of Moodle admin, select 'I can do these'.

  • I understand where the main site settings are and how to quickly find them
  • I understand how to improve the look and feel of my site
  • I understand how to manage the files my teachers and learners will upload.
